		(uuid "e400af23-c746-44a8-8740-868f397704cc")
	)
	(text "3. BMU-BQ79600\n\nCore function:\nBridges the MCU host interface to the external battery-monitor daisy-chain communication link.\n\nShort version for page 1:\n\nBQ79600 host-to-daisy-chain bridge\nInterfaces STM32 to external BQ79616 module chain\nHandles battery monitor communication link\n\nYou can also use this slightly clearer wording:\n\nInterfaces the MCU with the external battery monitoring daisy-chain network."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 292.608 71.12 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 2.032 2.032)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "3a0563fb-172d-4a3b-ac5d-65c9da6353b1")
	)
	(text "5. BMU-SHUNT\n\nCore function:\nMeasures pack current from the external shunt and reports it to the MCU.\n\nShort version for page 1:\n\nShunt-based current sensing interface\nAcquires pack current information\nSends current measurement data to MCU"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 293.37 151.892 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 2.032 2.032)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "6c9f66ba-1fd0-4b24-9ef7-8cee4ba120d9")
	)
	(text "4. BMU-CAN\n\nCore function:\nProvides physical CAN-FD bus interface between the BMU and vehicle ECU.\n\nShort version for page 1:\n\nCAN-FD transceiver interface\nConverts MCU CAN signals to vehicle bus levels\nConnects BMU to ECU / vehicle network\n"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 294.132 115.824 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 2.032 2.032)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "8c6e16ed-add1-41a2-b5c2-5c1af0afece8")
	)
	(text "2. BMU-MCU\n\nCore function:\nActs as the central controller for data processing, diagnostics, and system communication.\n\nShort version for page 1:\n\nMain STM32 controller\nExecutes BMU control and monitoring logic\nCommunicates with BQ interface, CAN, and current sensing circuits\nProvides debug and programming access"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 294.132 24.384 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 2.032 2.032)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "adf212c6-65c6-45fe-9126-33a46fa5c770")
	)
	(text "1. BMU-POWER\n\nCore function:\nConverts vehicle 12V input into regulated onboard supply rails for all BMU circuits.\n\nShort version for page 1:\n\n12V input conditioning and protection\nGenerates regulated 5V and 3.3V rails\nDistributes power to MCU, CAN, BQ interface, and sensing circuits"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 234.696 -14.986 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 2.032 2.032)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "d92171e3-4207-439c-8e4d-3e2560cdbd94")
	)
	(text "Optional module, if you keep it later\n6. BMU-SAFETY\n\nCore function:\nInterfaces BMU fault/status signals with external shutdown or safety-related control paths.\n\nShort version for page 1:\n\nSafety and shutdown interface\nFault/status signal routing\nOptional interface to shutdown and indicator circuits"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 292.608 193.04 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 2.032 2.032)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "fc614365-f0e9-419a-87c9-94d467b865a2")
	)
